StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: DELETEOFFICE
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.DELETEOFFICE(pOfficeNum IN VARCHAR2) AS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; DELETE FROM Office_table office&lt;br/&gt; WHERE office.officeNumber = pOfficeNum;&lt;br/&gt; COMMIT;&lt;br/&gt;END deleteOffice;
